name: Abiwasa Campsite
address: FGW9+C36, Jl. Tanah Ampo, Ulakan, Kec. Manggis, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80871, Indonesia
review 1: Amazing spot for camping or day-chilling, right in the middle of rice fields and a short walk from the beach. We love coming here for friends gatherings, guitar jams with freshly caught fish or chicken BBQ. And Wayan really does treat you like family!
review 2:
Wayan treats you like family.
We enjoyed fresh fish on the bbq and acoustic guitar with the beautiful sunset.

Do yourself a favour and check out this amazing location and destination!

Thank you Wayan and your family
review 3: A very friendly host and an even better cook. A visit will definitely be worth it with this great atmosphere
